# PS-3: Scope Control
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Any feature addition or expansion request

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Feature Creep: Uncontrolled expansion of product functionality.

ENFORCE: All scope changes require explicit approval; every addition must be logged with decision rationale.
PROHIBIT: Adding features without approval; silent scope expansion.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Product Governance Skill → halt unapproved implementation.
